        <h1>Trokam is great news for the world!</h1>

        <div class="container">

          <p class="fs-5">Trokam is an internet search engine. These are some of the unique features of Trokam:</p>

          <p class="fs-5"><strong>Ad-free</strong>. No advertisement at all!</p>

          <p class="fs-5"><strong>Transparency</strong>. You know how results are ranked.</p>

          <p class="fs-5"><strong>Free software</strong>. It is built entirely on <a href="https://github.com/trokam">open-source software.</a></p>

          <p class="fs-5"><strong>Privacy</strong>. Your searches are private.</p>

        </div>

        <h1 id="enhance-trokam">Join the most exciting software project of our time</h1>

        <div class="container">

          <p class="fs-5">These are some ways you can contribute:</p>

          <p class="fs-5"><strong>Donate</strong>. Trokam has a few machines indexing less than 1% of all Internet pages. Nevertheless, Trokam delivers valuable results. Trokam needs your contribution right now to reach more pages. <a href="/info/donate">You have several alternatives to contribute.</a></p>

          <p class="fs-5"><strong>Spread the word</strong>. Let others know about Trokam. Follow Trokam on <a href="https://twitter.com/trokam">Twitter</a> and <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/trokam/">LinkedIn</a>. Share and repost Trokam news.</p>

        </div>

